overview: Aliens from Outer Space (where else would they come from) Try and take over the world. Their plan : To animate all of the Earth's Dead into a work force. Then use that work force to take over the world,and eliminate all of mankind. Their only opposition Paula ,and Jeff Trent , A military man,and a seasoned Police Officer. Who will win the epic struggle ?
title: Plan 9.5 From Outerspace
